data.meta_description: Jan 28, 2024 - November 7, 2000: Her Majesty Ingrid of Sweden, Dowager Queen of Denmark died at 90 years old at Fredensborg Palace. Born Her Royal Highness Princess Ingrid of Sweden, she married the future King Frederick IX of Denmark in 1935 and the couple had three daughters. The late Queen is pictured with her daughters, Princess Benedikte, Princess Anne-Marie (now Her Majesty Queen Anne-Marie of Greece), and Princess Margrethe (now Her Majesty Queen Margrethe II of Denmark.
